Build in pause allows you to build while the game is paused. This is very handy when you're rebuilding a huge [[en/Manual/Stations|station]] or a mainline in your network while not disrupting any [[en/Manual/Trains|trains]] running on it.

However, this is no longer a patch feature, now it is considered as [[en/Manual/Cheats]]